features: 【USB-C Fast Charging-60W】: This c to c type fast charging cable supports PD 3.0 & QC 3.0 fast charging, Max output up to 20V/3A, suit with USB-C adapters. USB 2.0 supports data transfer speed up to 480Mbps. It efficiently charges your devices, such as laptops, smartphones, tablets, and other USB-C port devices, in a shorter amount of time compared to other cables.

【Just the Right Length - 6ft】: Neither insufficient like 3ft nor too long like 10ft, 6ft is just right for a variety of use cases. 3Pack 2-meter long fast charging cable allows you to charge your devices from a distance, whether you're on the sofa, in bed, or in the back seat of your car. It offers fast charging at home, in the office, or on the go, letting you work and charge your laptop or tablet anywhere.

【Safe and Stable, Nylon Braid】: Built-in E-marker smart chip provides full protection for device battery and adapter, giving you a faster, more stable and safer charging environment, making your phone and charging cables last longer. it can bear 20000+ bending test. High quality Nylon Braid material makes our USB C cable durable and strong while remaining flexible and tangle-free. The type c cable to type c fast charging has unique laser welding technology to make the connector prevent from broken.

【Widely compatible with USB-C devices】:The MFi Certified Type-C to Type-C 60W data cable can not only quickly charge Type-C phones, for iPhone 15/15 Pro/15 Pro Max/15 Plus, New iPad Mini, iPad Pro 12.9 in/ 11 in, iPad Air, Galaxy S23/S23+/S23 Ultra/S22/S22+/S22 Ultra/S21/S20/Note 20, Google Pixel, and more phones , but also support fast charging of Type-C laptops and tablets.

【Quality Commitment and Guarantee】: You will get 3pack MFi Certified fast charger cable. Our cable has a 3-year warranty, and we promise that as long as there are quality issues with the data cable, we will only replace it and not return it. At the same time, we support a 36 month product warranty and a 7-day 24-hour online service.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 20, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Don't get incompatible message when connecting it so it must be really Apple certified. The price is excellent, and the 10 foot length is fantastic. Can't go wrong, it looks sturdy too, like will last. Also it's a usbc to usbc so if you bought an Apple Vision Pro, it should work with it. Considering the one apple gives you with the Vision Pro is 2 meters (6 feet) you get an extra 4 feet with this one.
